                "text": "An anacite monitor can fade into the background by assuming the colors around them. When an anacite monitor remains stationary for 1 round, they gain a +10 circumstance bonus to Stealth checks. If they take any action, they lose this bonus until they once again spend 1 round remaining stationary.",
